{"type":null,"faqId":37114,"title":"Andriod微信公众号不能使用？（如何使用微信接入与好友一起PK运动排行？）运动数据同步到微信公众号（华为运动健康），提示微信已绑定或绑定失败怎么办？","answer":"<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">\n<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">\n<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" id=\"softwareDescription\" jQuery17106583258829874725=\"16\">\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">1、绑定微信“华为运动健康”公众号有两个通道：</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">（1）通过APP版本绑定微信“华为运动健康”公众号</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">a）ios版本</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">ios版本已经支持微信跳转功能，可以从该入口（APP右上角【设置-&gt;服务-&gt;微信接入】）跳转到微信客户端，如果你同步了数据，轻松点击最新排行，就可以与你的好友进行PK了。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">图示：</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><a href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/805e7_hbiij.png\" jQuery17106583258829874725=\"22\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/805e7_hbiij.png\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">b）Android版本其跳转入口在APP右上角【设置-&gt;服务-&gt;微信】。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">图示：</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><a href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/805e8_ffusx.png\" jQuery17106583258829874725=\"23\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/805e8_ffusx.png\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">点击“微信接入”启动微信客户端进入华为运动健康公众号界面，然后点击“关注”按钮即可完成接入。到此你就可以愉快地与好友进行运动排行PK了。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">（2）通过包装上的二维码扫描绑定微信“华为运动健康”公众号</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">打开微信，使用微信的扫一扫功能，扫描您手环包装上的手环二维码，添加公共账号“华为运动健康”</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">注意：</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">1）每个手环的微信二维码是唯一的，每个手环对应的微信二维码就是自己手环包装上的微信二维码，是一对一的关系。如果扫描并关注别人的二维码，会无法连接你的手环。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">2）当同时绑定多个手环设备时，微信公众号将从云端获取数字最大值进行显示。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">2、微信连接/绑定或同步失败解决措施：</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">1）确认之前是否关注“华为运动健康” 公众号（已经关注的请先暂时取消关注）</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">（问题APP版本号：2.5.2）2.6.0及其以后版本不存在问题</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">2）从APP右上角【设置-》服务-》微信-》微信接入】页面跳转到微信公众号，点击绑定关注</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">3）收到华为运动健康消息提示“账号信息绑定成功，解绑请取消关注”，说明您操作成功了</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">4）完成以上操作后每次使用APP的同步的数据都会自动出现在微信的排行榜里面呢~如果此时排行榜数据为0，请不要紧张，带着手环走几步直至app同步数据有增加，然后点击排行榜，数据就会出现。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">【小tips】：服务器暂时比较拥挤，数据可能会稍慢一点出现在微信里面，我们的攻城狮正在努力优化中，感谢您的理解~</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2278","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750143000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":268,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,死机,不开机,无法开机,自动关机,同步死机","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}